# EmbedFactory security allowlist — TEMPLATE.
# Copy this to  harness/allowed-roots  (that real file is gitignored and machine-specific).
# It is the trust anchor for the whole harness: anything NOT listed here is treated as an
# injection attempt by guard.sh and the sentinel.
#
# Two kinds of lines:
#   1. Absolute paths   = trusted PROJECT ROOTS. The active project must live under one of these.
#   2. remote:<prefix>  = trusted git remote URL PREFIXES. Clones / remotes must match one.
#
# Keep this list as TIGHT as possible. Examples (replace with your own — nothing here is baked
# into the committed harness):
#
# /Users/you/Documents/EmbeddedProjects
# remote:https://github.com/your-org/
# remote:git@github.com:your-org/
